{"tid":1385012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［不合作運動］今日一事 睇得出智商真係有高低之分","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:56:31.000Z","uid":121058,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0f4aaddaf83161001f03294842c37529391720","tid":1385012,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"知道今日有不合作運動 就專登偷雞遲D先起身<br />\n岩岩落街諗住食個早餐再慢慢番工<br />\n落到樓下商場就見到排哂隊 以為D人排接駁巴士<br />\n屌 原來成班人排緊隊食早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD食肆全部爆哂 最後去飲茶先有位 <br />\n睇到FB Live直播D啊叔爆哂粗 再望一望身邊D西裝友同我一樣仲慢慢咁嘆緊茶<br />\n番唔到工 有人就係地鐵屌鬼 有人就乘機嘆個慢板先<br />\n真係由心入面笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f951369a5d656f88c9501fc1c1ceebdbbfa282","tid":1385012,"uid":3549,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:47:32.000Z","msg":"傻鳩 有得賴都唔借d倚<br />\nd廢中廢老個腦都唔識轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc3e4bb72d447111cf209b02ce156e3f935da4c","tid":1385012,"uid":128522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"係地鐵睇到前面部電話<br />\n<br />\n首先係We7  同客講野既Group<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 西裝友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老細<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 對不起老闆，今天觀線線全掛了，真的趕不到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 對不起 _ 總，今天浪費了你時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 沒關係，咱們明天再談<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: XX 你還不快謝過 _ 總大人有大量?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 刷鞋<br />\n<br />\n轉個畫面去左同事Group<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 西裝友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同事A  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同事B<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 好野, 終於唔柒洗同個閪客開會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 屌你就爽啦，我果邊無人塞，死死地氣返左黎，結果成TEAM 人得我同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有老細係到你眼望我眼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咪就係，搞到我想上網睇餐廳都無人Cover，你條仆街仔今日仲唔請食TEA?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 傻架，我好努力咁返緊黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我決定繼續努力等車"},{"pid":"0f92e9410eddb1e0461006029c5478bbcdbf9d3f","tid":1385012,"uid":37443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f951369a5d656f88c9501fc1c1ceebdbbfa282","tid":1385012,"uid":3549,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:47:32.000Z","msg":"傻鳩 有得賴都唔借d倚<br />\nd廢中廢老個腦都唔識轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"無可否認有d可能係日工黎"},{"pid":"25fe7cc839fedbc77fa4cbd6eca5211285ce91e9","tid":1385012,"uid":253826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"人無分高低真係假嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec481512b06b7c2975f63f6bc4c7db795930c7e","tid":1385012,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"